{"tid":2022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻陰戶被老公詛咒 吸住姦夫陽具","createTime":"2016-11-25T17:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:06:30.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32211988a37b81ca1d0ed3e6293d29a7d73b0c6b","tid":2022,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:52:32.000Z","msg":"肯亞鄉鎮基希(Kisii)有一名人妻紅杏出牆，先前和小王做愛，她的陰戶卻深深吸住小王的陽具，讓小王抽不出生殖器。當地媒體報導指出，這都是因為老公請巫師作法，要給出軌的妻子懲罰。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這名人妻趁著老公出差不在家，與小王上床翻滾，結果兩人的生殖器緊緊相吸，小王的陰莖抽不出來，兩人在房裡大叫，驚動附近鄰居。鄰居隨後將兩人抬出，雖然兩人有用棉被包裹，但引來不少鄉民圍觀這對「姦夫淫婦」。當地媒體報導指出，其實人妻的老公早已知道老婆背著他出軌，為了懲罰說謊的妻子，於是請巫師作法，讓妻子的「鮑鮑」完全吸住小王的生殖器。<br />\n最後鄉民們把這對「姦夫淫婦」抬到巫師的住處，請巫師作法「解套」，人妻和小王才順利分開。不過另外有人認為，這種狀況與做法無關，而是一種醫學現象。<br />\n就有台灣網友專業解釋這種現象是「陰道痙攣症」，也有網友獻計「潑一桶冷水就分開了」，其他網友紛紛表示：「請巫師大人傳授我神術！」、「是聖嬰現象吧。」、「吸莖大法。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"640c9f576997fcb04eaae3774acffb6b61447fdb","tid":2022,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120f1c23498cdb29e0726409d8a08b8145bf5e81","tid":2022,"uid":11286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5d67fa2f5dd8cf33490d5b19b1bdd9c1669238","tid":2022,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5824cfd147b35c4429d47357ede1f2897d7cc73d","tid":2022,"uid":5247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:03:58.000Z","msg":"吸莖大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee427fb4ca95014a105d2a76f0b061e86d99b581","tid":2022,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8f77df8d1a109b2004d19ba4329f6722bfe731","tid":2022,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86074a558e838c050ca7de8ad41dfd1c153196f0","tid":2022,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}